#
#       README
#   mydns.jp updater
#
mydns_update is a software which updates mydns.jp DNS record.

INSTALL:
    Just run make:
        $ make
    or to specify Boost directory
        $ make BOOST_ROOT="your Boost dir"

RUN:
    $ ./mydns_update -f "your config file"
    A template of config file (mydns.conf) exists.

Requirements:
    C++11 compiler
    Boost C++ libraries
